        "subtype": "favored_weapon",
        "text": "*Breath of the Endless Sky*, *Cernunnos*, *Eiseth*, *Elion*, *Erastil*, *General Susumu*, *Hshurha*, *Isph-Aun-Vuln*, *Jukha*, *Ketephys*, *Phlegyas*, *Skode*, *Sky Keepers*, *Sovyrian Conclave*, *Ylimancha*",
